This section explains what legal basis used my Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP for each particular purpose of processing. For more information on a particular purpose, please refer to Section 2. This section applies only to EEA-based Users.
Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP processes EEA-based User’s personally identifiable data under the following legal bases: 
