3.2.	for other legitimate interests, unless those interests are overridden by User’s interests or fundamental rights and freedoms that require protection of personal data;
Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP rely on legitimate interests:
•	to communicate with User regarding User’s use of Service
This includes, for example, sending push notifications reminding to exercise at appropriate times. The legitimate interest Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP rely on for this purpose is interest to encourage User to use Service more often. Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP also take into account the potential benefits to User of following training, which may lead User to a better and healthier lifestyle.
•	to research and analyze User’s use of the Service
Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP’s legitimate interest for this purpose is interest in improving Service so Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP understands Users’ preferences and is able to provide User with a better experience.
•	to send marketing communications
The legitimate interest Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP rely on for this processing is interest to promote Service in a measured and appropriate way.
•	to personalize advertising
The legitimate interest Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP rely on for this processing is interest to promote Service in a reasonably targeted way.
•	to enforce Terms of Service and to prevent and combat fraud
Legitimate interests for this purpose are enforcing Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP’s legal rights, preventing and addressing fraud and unauthorised use of the Service, non-compliance with our Terms of Service.
3.3.	To comply with legal obligations.
