Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP share personally identifiable data with third parties  Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP hires to provide services or perform business functions on Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP’s behalf, based on instructions. Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP share User’s personal information with the following types of service providers:
•	measurement partners
