4.2.	Apple HealthKit or Google Fit (together the “Health App”)
Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP shares data about User’s activity with Health App applications installed on User’s device, provided that the User gave express permission on such device. Before User decide to share data with the Health App, Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP encourages the User to review the Health App’s privacy policies, as data will be subject to those policies. For more information on the Apple HealthKit, please see http://www.apple.com/ios/health/, and on the Google Fit, please see https://www.google.com/fit/.
