5.	EXERSICING OF PRIVACY RIGHTS
5.1.	To be in control of personal data, User have the following rights:
Accessing / reviewing / updating / correcting personally identifiable information. User may review, edit, or change the personal data that the one had previously provided to Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP in the profile section.
Deleting your personal data. User can request erasure of personally identifiable data by sending an email at smartfitness7@gmail.com. Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APPSmart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP
When User requested deletion of personally identifiable data, Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP will use reasonable efforts to honor such request. Any request will be answered within 1 month as of its filing. In some cases, Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP may be legally required to keep some portion of the personally identifiable data for a certain time. In such event, Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP will fulfill deletion request after obligations completed.
5.2.	 Additional information for EEA-based Users
5.2.1.	Users who based in the EEA have the following rights in addition to the above:
Right to rectification. User has the right to request to rectify, without undue delay, any incorrect data pertaining to the respective User.
Right to limitation of processing. User can limit the use of personally identifiable data collected.
Right of access. User may request a copy of personal data collected during use of the Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP at smartfitness7@gmail.com. 
Objecting to or restricting the use of personal identifiable data. User can ask to stop using all or some portion of personal identifiable data or limit use thereof by requesting its erasure as described above or sending a request at smartfitness7@gmail.com.
The right to lodge a complaint with supervisory authority. Users have the right to lodge a complaint with a competent data protection supervisory authority, in particular in the EU Member State where User reside, work or where the alleged infringement has taken place.
The right to data portability. User can receive personal identifiable data in a machine-readable format by send respective request at smartfitness7@gmail.com.
5.2.2.	Exercise the rights
To exercise their right to access User have the right to request from the Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP at any time:
-	Confirmation as to whether data related to them is processed by the Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP, the purpose of the processing, the data category, and recipients of such data or the categories of recipients’ data is disclosed to;
-	Information as to the logic of any automated processing of personally identifiable data pertaining to natural persons, at least in the case of automated decisions under the provisions of the GDPR. 
Upon request, Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP provides the information free of charge. However, Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP may charge a reasonable fee if request is clearly unfounded, repetitive or excessive. Alternatively, Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP may refuse to comply with User’s request in these circumstances.
The filing of the request is free of charge. 
Upon filing of a request by an authorised person, the notarised power of attorney must be attached to the request. 
In case of death of the natural person, his / her rights are exercised by his / her heirs and the certificate of heirs shall be attached to the request. The heritage should be confirmed by respective certificate, issued in the death person’s jurisdiction.
Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP shall review and pronounce on the request within 1 month as of its filing. This period may be extended by an additional two months, if necessary, for example, if User request is especially complex or User have made multiple requests. The Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP shall inform the User as to any such extension within 1 month as of receipt of the request, stating the reasons for the delay. When the User files a request by electronic means, the information is provided electronically, if possible, unless the User has requested otherwise.
Smart Fitness or one of the private branding of SMART WORKOUT APP provides an answer to the requesting person taking into account their preferred form for the provision of the information (orally or in writing - as a hard copy of electronically).
Where data do not exist or their provision is forbidden by law, access of the requesting party to such data is refused.
If the requesting party is not satisfied with the response received and / or believes that their rights related to personally identifiable data protection were violated, they are entitled to exercise their right to defence.
